.TH wxTopLevelWindow 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxTopLevelWindow \- \fIwxTopLevelWindow\fR is a common base class for \fIwxDialog\fR and \fIwxFrame\fR.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
It is an abstract base class meaning that you never work with objects of this class directly, but all of its methods are also applicable for the two classes above.

.PP
Note that the instances of \fIwxTopLevelWindow\fR are managed by wxWidgets in the internal top level window list.

.PP
See:


